constraint.sch:assert:
@uri attributes
                    must contain a properly formatted SPEAR factoid <div> URI that starts with
                    'http://syriaca.org/spear/'.

@ref attributes on
                    <persName> elements must contain a properly formatted Syriaca.org person URI
                    that starts with 'http://syriaca.org/person/'.

@ref attributes on
                    <placeName> elements must contain a properly formatted Syriaca.org place URI
                    that starts with 'http://syriaca.org/place/'.

sch:rule.sch:assert:
@target
                      attributes on <ptr> elements in an event factoid must point to a
                      Syriaca.org keyword starting with "http://syriaca.org/keyword/".

remarks.p:
This customization removes from the <relation> element all attributes except @name, @type, @ana, @mutual,
              @passive, and @active. It also restricts values for the @name, @type, and @ana
              attributes and requires the encoder to use the @name and @ana attributes.

constraint.sch:assert:
@ref attributes
                    on the <trait> element must point to a Syriaca.org keyword starting with
                    "http://syriaca.org/keyword/".
